{"tid":936160,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無恥的家人","createTime":"2018-12-10T14:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T09:21:01.000Z","uid":35324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa90f54d73e4b43222cb9a5a60aa46b3eb6e903","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"到而家我咁大個人，個老母斷斷續續養我嘅時間五年都唔夠<br />\n關係一路都冇好過<br />\n連埋個家姐 對住隻癲雞老母 成日都有野嘈<br />\n但我就唔會講咁多嘅，要癲嘅你地癲飽佢<br />\n<br />\n一嘈親 我個仆街家姐就同我講<br />\n你阿媽覺得對你唔住所以唔敢話你，你就話可以唔理走咗去，我就點都要氹返佢，因為佢係我阿媽<br />\n<br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆你個臭街啦，講到咁委屈<br />\n你幾十年人都跟住你老母<br />\n但呢個所謂老母比過啲咩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚偉大就係生咗我出嚟，又湊唔撚掂<br />\n<br />\n你憑咩成日冷嘲熱諷話我唔撚孝順佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b5e2ebcf4fc01392f0defa41476f4d48abde2e","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"咪撚話咩養兒防老吖<br />\n而家啲死廢物，唔撚使養就奉旨叫你&quot;報答&quot;返佢<br />\n<br />\n一有啲咩衣郁，就喊晒口話我係你老母嚟㗎，我咁錫你，你咁對我<br />\n<br />\n笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9966189cc6a28fdf44c76e05506544f5a7dc4624","tid":936160,"uid":177004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"你張回鄉咭守唔守得住？"},{"pid":"08cfaaddc808c87c9142ff2806f337a9a87a726a","tid":936160,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"咁樓主就唔好理佢地咁多啦<br />\n連累自己"},{"pid":"acdb27acae59048b6d7297184f8ac6bf69763d30","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9966189cc6a28fdf44c76e05506544f5a7dc4624","tid":936160,"uid":177004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"你張回鄉咭守唔守得住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"佢講咗要我張證嘅原因，但點解我就費事喺度講了<br />\n我冇得唔比<br />\n但決定以後唔會再搵佢（雖然原本都冇主動搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aac4c1f1de16d20858aa649b73a7c5debcac068","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08cfaaddc808c87c9142ff2806f337a9a87a726a","tid":936160,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"咁樓主就唔好理佢地咁多啦<br />\n連累自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"而家一個月都唔見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後會再減少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b4d1ede19152d6f5a1ec0b9f17889aa1fe92d5","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"唉 雖然我有啲唔開心<br />\n但我都唔知點解唔開心了<br />\n我根本不care佢地 話之佢死"},{"pid":"1073a7222800dc158cc5737a61e83fc3e6911352","tid":936160,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"你支旗仔又長左"},{"pid":"4d3a7f25d5ee8f4a23cef71078eb5a9bc71f143f","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"雖然我老母成日好似好好咁<br />\n話要錢就問我攞啦<br />\n多啲返嚟屋企食飯啦<br />\n<br />\n相見好(雖然一般)，同住難<br />\n佢就係嗰啲平時可以假仁假義下<br />\n但要佢揹返起個責任就唔肯嗰啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01850d113cde48fa1847c970ffd6fe40bf55fb02","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1073a7222800dc158cc5737a61e83fc3e6911352","tid":936160,"uid"