936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"雖然我老母成日好似好好咁<br />\n話要錢就問我攞啦<br />\n多啲返嚟屋企食飯啦<br />\n<br />\n相見好(雖然一般)，同住難<br />\n佢就係嗰啲平時可以假仁假義下<br />\n但要佢揹返起個責任就唔肯嗰啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"女人係咁 幾口是心非<br />\n其實有時真係面子同自私係度搏鬥緊<br />\n我會咁睇 唉,阿媽你已經受到你應有既懲罰<br />\n無勞都有功 我會盡我能力去照顧你下半世<br />\n旗仔,有時做好人唔一定係對外既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9608082bd265550a82bfa5336759f9ee8da62919","tid":936160,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc99e5ada381c1c4074f3daaad05e533025c4a0","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14dc4939abc0af3b6b0f35d082995d27c67cb40","tid":936160,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01850d113cde48fa1847c970ffd6fe40bf55fb02","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見騎士仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"你成日都唔黎開PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"我開好多wor，你追蹤我就可以即刻見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"唔通成日都唔岩時段??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8c2f55676dda92d26660eb021b6bafb6324823","tid":936160,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc99e5ada381c1c4074f3daaad05e533025c4a0","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14dc4939abc0af3b6b0f35d082995d27c67cb40","tid":936160,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01850d113cde48fa1847c970ffd6fe40bf55fb02","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見騎士仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"你成日都唔黎開PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"我開好多wor，你追蹤我就可以即刻見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"好,追左"},{"pid":"a808bbe47ed004c0ec38163ace7b8f86646af869","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然我老母成日好似好好咁<br />\n話要錢就問我攞啦<br />\n多啲返嚟屋企食飯啦<br />\n<br />\n相見好(雖然一般)，同住難<br />\n佢就係嗰啲平時可以假仁假義下<br />\n但要佢揹返起個責任就唔肯嗰啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>女人係咁 幾口是心非<br />\n其實有時真係面子同自私係度搏鬥緊<br />\n我會咁睇 唉,阿媽你已經受到你應有既懲罰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無勞都有功 我會盡我能力去照顧你下半世</span><br />\n旗仔,有時做好人唔一定係對外既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個我同你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e24487360dca566a227d47914f9ac1b211bb650","tid":936160,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aac4c1f1de16d20858aa649b73a7c5debcac068","tid":936160,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08cfaaddc808c87c9142ff2806f337a9a87a726a","tid":936160,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"咁樓主就唔好理佢地咁多啦<br />\n連累自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"而家一個月都唔見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後會再減少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"咁就岩啦<br />\n搬出黎 搵人夾租<br />\n寧願捱幾年都唔好比人累成世"}]}